originalText.text:
Test Prep San Francisco is a game changer for students hoping to secure a competitive score on their admissions tests, and gain peace of mind when going in to take their tests. No one really addresses this need from what I've found in the field, and I'm happy I have a go-to company to send my students to.

One-on-one tutoring is an investment, but if you're looking for the best return, and seek optimal results, definitely consider TPSF. Among their strengths is their emphasis on matching each student with the most appropriate tutor suited to meet the individual's intellectual and emotional needs. TPSF worked with my client, an SAT student who had a lot of anxiety prior going into her test. In one session, they were able to allay her fears, and she was able to enter and take the test without feeling overwhelmed or nervous. Plus, they made sure her knowledge base was up to snuff. TPSF is committed to each student's success and Bara Sapir who runs the operation is knowledgeable, responsive and effective.
